          <h3>Travel to and from the airport</h3>

          <p>If you are flying into Copenhagen you will arrive at and depart from Copenhagen Airport (CPH). The easiest way to get to Central Copenhagen is by taking the <strong>Metro M2 line</strong> to <strong>Nørreport station</strong>.</p>
          <p>When you exit the arrival area in the airport (Terminal 3), simply to continue straight ahead until you see the Metro signs. Take the escalator one level up. On the station platform you should be able to buy a Zone 4 ticket, which takes you down town. The trains departs every 10th minute, so don't worry if you miss a train.</p>

